title: Mozart - The Violin Concertos - Szeryng, Gibson, NPO
description:
Mozart: The Five Violin Concertos.

These performances of 19 year old Mozart's beautiful Violin Concertos were so perfectly performed by Henryk Szeryng (violin) and the New Philharmonia Orchestra, conducted by Sir Alexander Gibson, that Philips chose these late 1960s recordings to include in their Complete Mozart Edition of 1991.

Please enjoy.

MP3 @ 320
